    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it's just so many pills and they make my stomach feel kinda weird and nauseous. if the visible sign of the infection is gone, isn't it basically just unnecessary chemicals at this point? i've heard that taking them too long can actually mess with your gut microbiome more than the infection itself. wouldn't it be safer to just stop now that the symptoms are gone?",
