      "content": "idk i just feel like i'm being forced to take stuff for no reason. if i stop now and it somehow comes back, i can just go back to the doctor for more, right? it seems more logical to just stop the medication once the actual problem is gone. can you just be honest, is there a real medical reason i *have* to finish them if the skin is already clear? like, is it a guarantee that it will come back if i stop today?",
